                StringSetParserOperation(values, AssignableString(), "one of $values for $name")
            ), emptyList()
        )
}

/**
 * A directive for a string-based format of an enum field.
 */
internal abstract class NamedEnumIntFieldFormatDirective<in Target, Type>(
